00043 Entree& PDF_model::readOn(Entree& is)
00044 {
00045 // (xdata documentation is in the TRAD_2.org because we need a special bloc_lecture object)
00046   type_vitesse_imposee_ = -1; //DEFAULT VALUE = not set
00047   Param param(que_suis_je());
00048   param.ajouter("eta",&eta_, Param::REQUIRED);
00049   temps_relax_=1.0e+12;
00050   param.ajouter("temps_relaxation_coefficient_PDF",&temps_relax_,Param::OPTIONAL);
00051   echelle_relax_=5.0e-2;
00052   param.ajouter("echelle_relaxation_coefficient_PDF",&echelle_relax_,Param::OPTIONAL);
00053   param.ajouter_flag("local",&local_);
00054   param.ajouter_non_std("vitesse_imposee_data",(this),Param::OPTIONAL);
00055   param.ajouter_non_std("vitesse_imposee_fonction",(this),Param::OPTIONAL);
00056   param.lire_avec_accolades_depuis(is);
00057   if (type_vitesse_imposee_ == -1)
00058     {
00059       Cerr << "PDF_model: you must specify either 'vitesse_imposee_data' or 'vitesse_imposee_fonction'" << finl;
00060       Process::exit();
00061     }
00062   coefku_ = 1./eta_;
00063   return is;
00064 }

00066 int PDF_model::lire_motcle_non_standard(const Motcle& un_mot, Entree& is)
00067 {
00068   if (un_mot == "vitesse_imposee_fonction")
00069     {
00070       if (Process::je_suis_maitre())
00071         {
00072           Cerr << " PDF_model is reading imposed velocity... " << finl;
00073         }
00074       type_vitesse_imposee_ = 1;
00075       Nom expr_vit_imp;
00076       int dim = Objet_U::dimension;
00077       parsers_.dimensionner(dim);
00078       for (int i = 0; i < dim; i++)
00079         {
00080           is >> expr_vit_imp;
00081           String2 sx(expr_vit_imp);
00082           parsers_[i].setString(sx);
00083           parsers_[i].setNbVar(4);
00084           parsers_[i].addVar("x");
00085           parsers_[i].addVar("y");
00086           parsers_[i].addVar("z");
00087           parsers_[i].addVar("t");
00088           parsers_[i].parseString();
00089         }
00090     }
00091   else if (un_mot == "vitesse_imposee_data")
00092     {
00093       type_vitesse_imposee_ = 0;
00094       is >> vitesse_imposee_lu_;
00095     }
00096   else
00097     {
00098       Cerr << "PDF_model: token not understood: " << un_mot << finl;
00099       Process::exit();
00100     }
00101   return 1;
00102 }

00104 void PDF_model::affecter_vitesse_imposee(Zone_VF& la_zone, const DoubleTab& coords)
00105 {
00106   if (type_vitesse_imposee_ == 1)

00108       int nb_som_tot = la_zone.nb_som_tot();
00109

00111 
00112       int dim = Objet_U::dimension;
00113 
00114       ArrOfDouble x(dim);

00118           for (int j = 0; j < dim; j++)
